  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Keil and Delitzsch Biblical Commentary on the Old Testament",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And had ordained him priests for the high places. ויּעמד־לו is a continuation of הזניחם כּי, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 11:14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". בּמות are the places of worship which were erected by Jeroboam for the image-worship, called in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 12:31",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
